01:32:49.105 --> 01:32:50.903
EUGENE: No man, I'll check
with her. It should be good.

01:32:51.191 --> 01:32:52.659
RYAN:
No, it's okay.

01:32:52.942 --> 01:32:56.367
EUGENE: Bud, we'll
